                <note xml:id="foot.f2">CD wrote that he preferred the lien, but was willing to be advised otherwise by Higgins (<hi rend="italic">Correspondence</hi> vol. 6, <ref target="./DCP-LETT-1993.xml">letter to John Higgins, 19 November [1856]</ref>).</note>
            </div>
        
